* INSTALL
First of all, you need mecab installed.

If you check out the source from the repository, you need autoconf, automake and libtool 
to build the plugin. Type as following:
$ aclocal
$ libtoolize --automake
$ automake --add-missing
$ automake
$ autoconf

Then you start a normal installation process.
$ ./configure --with-mysql-config=/path/to/mysql_config --with-mecab-config=/path/to/mecab-config
$ make
# make install

